{"name":"Hermione Granger","nameCn":"赫敏·格兰杰","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/m/6b/0b/75759_crt_tdvy3.jpg","info":"<li><span>简体中文名: </span>赫敏·格兰杰</li><li><span>别名: </span>赫敏·简·格兰杰</li><li><span style=\"visibility:hidden;\">别名: </span>Hermione Jean Granger</li><li><span>性别: </span>女</li><li><span>生日: </span>1979年9月19日</li><li><span>引用来源: </span>harrypotter.fandom.com/zh/wiki</li><li><span>出生地区: </span>英国</li>","detail":"赫敏·格兰杰（港澳台作妙丽·格兰杰）是英国作家乔安·凯瑟琳·罗琳的奇幻小说《哈利·波特》系列中的登场人物，女主角兼三个核心人物之一，与哈利·波特和罗恩·韦斯莱为挚交好友。<br /><br />她是麻瓜格兰杰夫妇的独生女，他们一家人居住在伦敦。十一岁时，赫敏得知自己是一个女巫，需要去霍格沃茨魔法学校上学。她在1991年9月1日进入学校读书，被分进格兰芬多学院。她精通学术、用功好学，被认为是天才，但是同时又有些书呆子气。和哈利·波特还有其他一些人一样，赫敏很少会被伏地魔的名字吓倒，敢于直呼其名，而不是使用“神秘人”或者“那个连名字都不能提的魔头”。","jobs":[{"href":"/subject/78306","name":"Harry Potter","nameCn":"哈利·波特","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/51/5a/78306_qhf59.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":1},{"href":"/subject/194039","name":"Harry Potter and the Cursed Child","nameCn":"哈利·波特与被诅咒的孩子","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/d8/85/194039_us.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"","castHref":"","castTag":"","castCover":"","type":1},{"href":"/subject/60105","name":"Harry Potter and the Half-Blood Prince","nameCn":"哈利·波特与混血王子","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/3d/c0/60105_4T7t2.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Emma Watson","castHref":"/person/23742","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/87/00/23742_prsn_6W66h.jpg","type":6},{"href":"/subject/60107","name":"Harry Potter and the Goblet of Fire","nameCn":"哈利·波特与火焰杯","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/17/8b/60107_EXHDm.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Emma Watson","castHref":"/person/23742","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/87/00/23742_prsn_6W66h.jpg","type":6},{"href":"/subject/60106","name":"Harry Potter and the Order of the Phoenix","nameCn":"哈利·波特与凤凰社","cover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/cover/g/39/d9/60106_ywuCM.jpg","staff":"主角","cast":"Emma Watson","castHref":"/person/23742","castTag":"CV","castCover":"//lain.bgm.tv/pic/crt/s/